<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><br/></div><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>1. Consistent with macromastia (hypertrophy of the breast), right breast</div><div>2. Consistent with macromastia (hypertrophy of the breast), left breast</div><div>Bilateral reduction mammaplasty</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>GROSS DESCRIPTION:</div><div>#1. [Right breast] It measures 17 x 10 x 7 cm and 344 gm with overlying skin measuring</div><div>    10 x 5 cm. No tumor is seen.</div><div>#2. [Left breast] It measures 14 x 9 x 5 cm and 313.5 gm with overlying skin measuring</div><div>    8 x 6 cm. No tumor is seen.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Representative sections are taken and labeled as follows:</div><div>RA-RC: right breast</div><div>RD-RF: left breast</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>MICROSCOPIC FINDING:</div><div>Sections show skin and normal fibroglandular breast tissue. No malignancy is observed.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
