weak / moderate / strong) </div><div><span style="color:red;">Progesterone receptor:</span> Positive Negative (_%,
weak / moderate / strong) </div><div><span style="color:red;">pTNM</span>: pTis (AJCC cancer
staging system, 8th edition)</div><div>TNM descriptors: Not applicable.</div><div> </div><div>(This case has been reviewed by two
pathologists.)</div><hr/><div>There is a _ cm well healed surgical scar in the _ quadrant, _ cm from the nipple. </div><div><br/></div><div>There is a biopsy_excisional cavity (_ x _ x _ cm) filled with red_brown organizing thrombus which is located _ cm deep to the scar. The cavity is surrounded by firm white tissue, with no residual tumor identified grossly. The cavity is _ cm from the deep margin and _ cm from the nearest lateral margin.</div></en-note>      ]]>
