  <note>
    <title>FZ at least AIS [lung]</title>
    <created>20210709T030940Z</created>
    <updated>20250603T043400Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Temporary Pathological Diagnosis :</div><div>Lung, ___, frozen biopsy</div><div>-- At least adenocarcinoma in situ.</div><div>-- Margin free.</div><div><br/></div><div>Further sampling is needed to exclude invasion.</div><div>Please follow the pathology report of the subsequent</div><div>permanent specimen for a definitive diagnosis.</div><div><br/></div><div>Gross description:</div><div>The specimen consists of a piece of wedge-resected lung</div><div>tissue measuring _ cm and_  gm. On cut section,</div><div>a tumor measuring _ cm is seen..</div><div><br/></div><div>Representative sections are taken for frozen section:</div><div>A: tumor</div><div>B: margin</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
