<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>Papillary carcinoma, thyroid, _lobe , intraoperative consultation</div><div style="margin-top: 1em;margin-bottom: 1em;-en-paragraph:true;"><br clear="none" /></div><div>FROZEN SECTION REPORT: same as above</div><div style="margin-top: 1em;margin-bottom: 1em;-en-paragraph:true;"><br clear="none" /></div><div><span>    </span><br/></div><div style="margin-top: 1em;margin-bottom: 1em;-en-paragraph:true;"><br clear="none" /></div><div>GROSS DESCRIPTION:</div><div>Received is a lobe of thyroid measuring _ x _ x _ cm. A firm, whitish tumor is seen measuring _ cm in maximum dimension. </div><div>A representative section is taken for frozen section and is then submitted for permanent section.</div><div style="margin-top: 1em;margin-bottom: 1em;-en-paragraph:true;"><br clear="none" /></div><div>The tissue is totally embedded for frozen section and then fixed in formalin for paraffin embedding.</div><div><br clear="none" /></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>FZ Skin</title>
    <created>20150723T235519Z</created>
    <updated>20230919T032835Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>DIAGNOSIS:<br clear="none" />Free margin, _, skin, intraoperative consultation</div><div><br clear="none" /></div><div>FROZEN SECTION REPORT: same as above<p><br clear="none" /></p><div><span>Note: Please follow the pathology report (201_-_-_) of the subsequent permanent </span><br clear="none" /><span>specimen for a definitive diagnosis.</span></div><div><br clear="none" /></div></div><div>REFERENCE:<br clear="none" />PREVIOUS PATHOLOGIC EXAMS:</div><div><br clear="none" />GROSS DESCRIPTION:<br clear="none" />The specimen consists of one fragment of skin, measuring _ x _ x _ cm with two _long strands indicating the 12 o'clock and two _short strands indicating the 6 o'clock.<br clear="none" />A ___tumor is seen, measuring _ x _ x _ cm. <br clear="none" />It measures _ cm to 12 o'clock, _ cm to 3 o'clock, _ cm to 6 o'clock and _ to 9 o'clock surgical margins, respectively.</div><p><br clear="none" /></p><div>One representative section of the tumor and 9 and 3 o'clock margin is taken for frozen examination.<br clear="none" /></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>FZ SLN</title>
    <created>20150723T235104Z</created>
    <updated>20230612T045921Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>Negative for metastasis (_/_), right/ left axillary sentinel lymph node /s, intraoperative</div><div>consultation</div><div><br/></div><div>FROZEN SECTION REPORT: same as above</div><div><br/></div><div>Note: Please follow the pathology report (201_-_-_) of the subsequent permanent</div><div>specimen for a definitive diagnosis.</div><div><br clear="none" /></div><div>GROSS DESCRIPTION:</div><div>There is/are _ container/s sent for intraoperative consultation. The first container</div><div>is composed of _ fragment/s of adipose tissue, measuring _ x _ x _ cm in total. _ lymph</div><div>node/s is/are dissected out and measuring _ x _ x _ cm.</div><div>The other container is composed of _ fragment/s of adipose tissue, measuring (up to)</div><div>_ x _ x _ cm (in total). _ lymph nodes/ is/are dissected out, measuring _ cm and/to _ cm in greatest dimension.</div><div><br/></div><div>The sentinel lymph nodes are sliced and totally embedded for</div><div>frozen section and then fixed in formalin for paraffin embedding.</div><div style="margin-top: 1em;margin-bottom: 1em;-en-paragraph:true;">精簡版: Received is a fragment of fat tissue with one lymph node dissected out measuring 1.9 cm in maximum dimension.</div><div>    <span>    </span></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
