    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><br/></div><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>Consistent with pneumothorax, lung, __, wedge resection</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>GROSS DESCRIPTION:</div><div>The specimen is composed of one piece of brown tissue, measuring     x      x      cm.</div><div><br/></div><div>All are embedded in one cassette.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>MICROSCOPIC DESCRIPTION:</div><div>Section shows focal emphysematous change and focal fresh hemorrhage. These features are consistent with pneumothorax. There is no evidence of malignancy.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
