  <note>
    <title>Uterus (micro descriptions)</title>
    <created>20150723T090342Z</created>
    <updated>20250318T032126Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>.Leiomyoma / leiomyomata and adenomyosis, myometrium</div><div>. Chronic cervicitis, uterine cervix</div><div>. Proliferative / Secretory / Inactive phase, endometrium</div><div>. Within normal limit, right / left / bilateral adnexa</div><div>. Serous cyst / Mucinous cyst / Corpus luteal cyst / Corpus luteum hematoma / Endometrioma, right / left ovary</div><div>. Within normal limit, right / left / bilateral ovary(ies)</div><div>. Hydrosalpinx, right / left / bilateral fallopian tube(s)</div><div>. Within normal limit, right / lDeft / bilateral fallopian tube(s)</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Laparoscopic assisted vaginal hysterectomy and bilateral salpingectomy</div><div>Abdominal total hysterectomy</div><div>Complicated total abdominal hysterectomy</div><div><br/></div><div>GROSS DESCRIPTION:</div><div>The specimen submitted is a uterus with bilateral _adnexa/ fallopian tubes. The uterus</div><div>measures _ x _ x _ cm and _ gm. On cut section, the endometrium and</div><div>myometrium measure _ cm and _ cm respectively. __ intramural myomatous nodules are seen,</div><div>measuring (up to) _ x _ x _ cm. On cut sections, whorls of whitish fibrous tissue is noted.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>The attached adnexa consists of one segment of fallopian tube measuring _ x _ cm in</div><div>length and diameter, respectively, and the ovary measuring _ x _ x _ cm.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Right fallopian tube measures _ x _ cm in length and diameter, respectively.</div><div>Left fallopian tube measures _ x _ cm in length and diameter, respectively.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>The right fallopian tube measures ___ x ___ cm in length and diameter respectively. The right ovary measures ___ x ___ x ___ cm. Its external surface is smooth and glistening.</div><div>The left fallopian tube measures ___ x ___ cm in length and diameter respectively. The left ovary measures ___ x ___ x ___ cm. Its external surface is smooth and glistening.</div><div><br/></div><div>Representative sections are taken and labeled as follows:</div><div>A1: cervix</div><div>A2: endometrium and myometrium</div><div>A3: myomatous nodules</div><div><br/></div><div>MICROSCOPIC FINDINGS:</div><div>The uterine cervix shows chronic inflammatory infiltrate with squamous metaplasia.</div><div>The endometrium reveals glands in proliferative phase.</div><div>The myomatous nodules are composed of spindle-shaped cells arranged in interlacing fascicles with focal degenerative change.</div><div><br/></div><div>The myometrium shows embedded endometrial glands and stromal cells. </div><div><br/></div><div>The _ ovary shows entrapped endometrial glands and stromal     cells, accompanied by hemosiderin-laden macrophages in the stroma.</div><div>The _ ovary shows a cystic lesion with hemosiderin-laden marcropahges and granulation tissue in the wall.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
